title: WiseCleaner Wise Hotkey v1.13
description:
WiseCleaner Wise Hotkey v1.13

App Launcher & Switcher for Windows

Wise Hotkey is a simple and easy- to-use program that can help you improve the efficiency of using computer. It can implement that quick start or quick switch any application, folder or website by using keyboard shortcuts.

Quick launch any application, folder or website
When we use computer in our daily life, we run certain programs every time. With Wise Hotkey, you can launch these applications by keyboard shortcuts. It saves time to find and mouse click. Users not only can add frequently used applications, but also can add folders or URLs.
